Class ParticipantProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.outrigger.proxy.ParticipantProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Remote, net.jini.core.transaction.server.TransactionConstants, net.jini.core.transaction.server.TransactionParticipant, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstrainableParticipantProxy

    public class ParticipantProxy
extends Object
implements net.jini.core.transaction.server.TransactionParticipant, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid, Serializable
    Object Outrigger hands to transaction managers on join. Passes through TransactionParticipant calls to the inner proxy and provides implementations of equals and hashCode that do reference equality.
    Author:
    Sun Microsystems, Inc.
